	(CMM). A scan of the field provides the components of the field vector
	w.r.t. the coordinates of the CMM reference frame. However, assembly
	tolerances of the sensor impair the field measurement. This paper
	explains a calibration procedure how to determine the misalignment
	of the sensor w.r.t. the reference frame of the CMM. To this end,
